sert', '["Boost energy","Eating a balanced diet"]', '["Diabetes","High blood pressure","Kidney disease"]', 'https://exscmqdazkrtrfhstytk.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/dishes/turon.jpg'), ('28', 'Banana Cue', '1', 'Deep-fried caramelized bananas coated in brown sugar and skewered on sticks. A popular street food snack in the Philippines, sweet and crunchy.', null, 'Balance', '["Skewer saba bananas","Roll in brown sugar","Deep-fry until caramelized"]', 'Snack/Dessert', '["Boost energy","Eating a balanced diet"]', '["Diabetes","High blood pressure","Kidney disease"]', 'https://exscmqdazkrtrfhstytk.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/dishes/banana%20cue.jpg'), ('29', 'Champorado', '1', 'Chocolate rice porridge made with sticky rice and cocoa, often served with milk or paired with salted fish. Comforting and sweet, commonly eaten for breakfast.', null, 'Balance', '["Boil glutinous rice in water","Add cocoa powder or tablea; stir until thick","Sweeten with sugar; serve hot with milk"]', 'Breakfast', '["Boost energy","Managing stress","Eating a balanced diet"]', '["Diabetes","High blood pressure","Kidney disease"]', 'https://exscmqdazkrtrfhstytk.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/dishes/champorado.jpg'), ('30', 'Arroz Caldo', '1', 'Rice porridge with chicken, flavored with ginger and garlic, often topped with fried garlic and scallions.', null, 'Balance', '["Sauté garlic, onion, and ginger","Add chicken; cook until lightly browned","Pour in rice and water/broth; simmer until rice is soft","Season with fish sauce; top with fried garlic and green onions"]', 'Breakfast', '["Boost energy","Managing stress","Eating a balanced diet"]', '["Diabetes","High blood pressure","Kidney disease"]', 'https://exscmqdazkrtrfhstytk.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/dishes/arozcaldo.jpg'), ('31', 'Goto', '1', 'Savory rice porridge made with beef tripe and ginger, commonly served as a hearty breakfast or snack.', null, 'Balance', '["Boil beef tripe until tender","Sauté garlic, oni